   <ReleaseDate>2020-06-01T20:24:53Z</ReleaseDate>
   <Description>Level 1D files contain a thumbnail image (PNG) for total Lyman-Birge-Hopfield (LBH) radiance.
   A new L1D file is generated for each new L1C file. These correspond to either the Northern or Southern hemisphere.
   Individual image size = 512 x 512 pixels. Total LBH brightness map (in Rayleighs) integrates the signal from 
   137 to 155 nm with 148.5 to 150.0 nm masked.</Description>
